ry. Look, your flags are flying in every corner. Congratulations! You are an excellent strategist.\n\nKey Features:\n- An immersive battle experience as a leader\n- Think strategically to conduct sieges and expand territories\n- Interesting interactive scenes, our lovely animals come to cheer for you\n- Hundreds of levels with the equipment upgrade system\n- To observe our table at a close distance for more details to discover\n\nWe will continue to iterate and update our game, including Online mode, Richer and cooler special effects, and Various battle scenes. Contact and find more info on Discord: https://discord.gg/xyZbrkjGZK\n\nGood luck!", "short_description": "Fight and conquer for your state as the head of an army!\nJoin this battle of wit! Enemy troops have arrived at the gate of your hold that might fall into pieces at any moment. Block and occupy enemy towers while strengthen your own, then you shall have an epic victory. \nFeatures:\n- An immersive battle experience as a leader\n- Our lovely animals bring fun interaction to cheer for you\n- Hundreds of levels with the equipment upgrade system\n- To discover more details at a close distance\nGood Luck!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://stateconquer.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "SUPLIFE PTE", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://stateconquer.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["PUZZLE", "STRATEGY", "CASUAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "u